Effect The troop attacks enemies within 5 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:21|basic:true]), with damage depending on the number of actions.

1 @Damage[(1d6+3)[bludgeoning]] damage

2 @Damage[(2d10+6)[bludgeoning]] damage

3 @Damage[(2d10+9)[bludgeoning]] damage

Whenever the ghostly mob Strides, it first Forms Up as a free action to condense into a 20-foot-by-20-foot area (minus any missing squares), and then moves. This works just like a Gargantuan creature moving; for instance, if any of the ghostly mob's squares enter difficult terrain, the extra movement cost applies to the whole group.

When at first t hrshold commoner gets a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.7blmbDrQFNfdT731]{Shove}, attack rolls, and damage rolls, which lowers to +1 at 2nd threshold, and 0 at 3rd threshold.
